{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"ms2\">R\u00c8GNE DE SALOMON<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"mr\">Ch. 1 \u00e0 11. (2 Ch 1 \u00e0 9.) (2 S 7:12-15. Ps 89.)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">Vieillesse du roi David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-4: cf. (Ec 12:3-7; 4:11.) Ps 45:11, 12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Le roi David \u00e9tait vieux, avanc\u00e9 en \u00e2ge; on le couvrait de v\u00eatements, et il ne pouvait se r\u00e9chauffer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.2","name":"1 Rois 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.25","name":"2 Samuel 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Ses serviteurs lui dirent: Que l\u2019on cherche pour mon seigneur le roi une jeune fille vierge; qu\u2019elle se tienne devant le roi, qu\u2019elle le soigne, et qu\u2019elle couche dans ton sein; et mon seigneur le roi se r\u00e9chauffera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.3","name":"1 Rois 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.1","name":"1 Rois 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>On chercha dans tout le territoire d\u2019Isra\u00ebl une fille jeune et belle, et on trouva Abischag, la Sunamite, que l\u2019on conduisit aupr\u00e8s du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.4","name":"1 Rois 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.2","name":"1 Rois 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Cette jeune fille \u00e9tait fort belle. Elle soigna le roi, et le servit; mais le roi ne la connut point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.5","name":"1 Rois 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.3","name":"1 Rois 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Adonija, l\u2019un de ses fils, aspirant \u00e0 la royaut\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 5-10: cf. 2 S 15:1-12. Ro 12:3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Adonija, fils de Haggith, se laissa emporter par l\u2019orgueil jusqu\u2019\u00e0 dire: C\u2019est moi qui serai roi! Et il se procura un char et des cavaliers, et cinquante hommes qui couraient devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.6","name":"1 Rois 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.4","name":"1 Rois 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Son p\u00e8re ne lui avait de sa vie fait un reproche, en lui disant: Pourquoi agis-tu ainsi? Adonija \u00e9tait, en outre, tr\u00e8s beau de figure, et il \u00e9tait n\u00e9 apr\u00e8s Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.7","name":"1 Rois 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.5","name":"1 Rois 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il eut un entretien avec Joab, fils de Tseruja, et avec le sacrificateur Abiathar; et ils embrass\u00e8rent son parti.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.8","name":"1 Rois 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.6","name":"1 Rois 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Mais le sacrificateur Tsadok, Benaja, fils de Jehojada, Nathan le proph\u00e8te, Schime\u00ef, R\u00e9\u00ef, et les vaillants hommes de David, ne furent point avec Adonija.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.9","name":"1 Rois 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.7","name":"1 Rois 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Adonija tua des brebis, des b\u0153ufs et des veaux gras, pr\u00e8s de la pierre de Zoh\u00e9leth, qui est \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 d\u2019En-Roguel; et il invita tous ses fr\u00e8res, fils du roi, et tous les hommes de Juda au service du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.10","name":"1 Rois 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.8","name":"1 Rois 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Mais il n\u2019invita point Nathan le proph\u00e8te, ni Benaja, ni les vaillants hommes, ni Salomon, son fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.11","name":"1 Rois 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.9","name":"1 Rois 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-31: cf. (1 Ch 17:11-15; 22:6-13.) Pr 16:10, 12. 2 Co 1:17-20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Alors Nathan dit \u00e0 Bath-Sch\u00e9ba, m\u00e8re de Salomon: N\u2019as-tu pas appris qu\u2019Adonija, fils de Haggith, est devenu roi, sans que notre seigneur David le sache?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.12","name":"1 Rois 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.10","name":"1 Rois 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Viens donc maintenant, je te donnerai un conseil, afin que tu sauves ta vie et la vie de ton fils Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.13","name":"1 Rois 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.11","name":"1 Rois 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Va, entre chez le roi David, et dis-lui: O roi mon seigneur, n\u2019as-tu pas jur\u00e9 \u00e0 ta servante, en disant: Salomon, ton fils, r\u00e9gnera apr\u00e8s moi, et il s\u2019assi\u00e9ra sur mon tr\u00f4ne? Pourquoi donc Adonija r\u00e8gne-t-il?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.14","name":"1 Rois 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.12","name":"1 Rois 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et voici, pendant que tu parleras l\u00e0 avec le roi, j\u2019entrerai moi-m\u00eame apr\u00e8s toi, et je compl\u00e9terai tes paroles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.15","name":"1 Rois 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.13","name":"1 Rois 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Bath-Sch\u00e9ba se rendit dans la chambre du roi. Il \u00e9tait tr\u00e8s vieux; et Abischag, la Sunamite, le servait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.16","name":"1 Rois 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.14","name":"1 Rois 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Bath-Sch\u00e9ba s\u2019inclina et se prosterna devant le roi. Et le roi dit: Qu\u2019as-tu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.17","name":"1 Rois 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.15","name":"1 Rois 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Elle lui r\u00e9pondit: Mon seigneur, tu as jur\u00e9 \u00e0 ta servante par l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, en disant: Salomon, ton fils, r\u00e9gnera apr\u00e8s moi, et il s\u2019assi\u00e9ra sur mon tr\u00f4ne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.18","name":"1 Rois 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.16","name":"1 Rois 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et maintenant voici, Adonija r\u00e8gne! Et tu ne le sais pas, \u00f4 roi mon seigneur!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.19","name":"1 Rois 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.17","name":"1 Rois 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Il a tu\u00e9 des b\u0153ufs, des veaux gras et des brebis en quantit\u00e9; et il a invit\u00e9 tous les fils du roi, le sacrificateur Abiathar, et Joab, chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e, mais il n\u2019a point invit\u00e9 Salomon, ton serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.20","name":"1 Rois 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.18","name":"1 Rois 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>O roi mon seigneur, tout Isra\u00ebl a les yeux sur toi, pour que tu lui fasses conna\u00eetre qui s\u2019assi\u00e9ra sur le tr\u00f4ne du roi mon seigneur apr\u00e8s lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.21","name":"1 Rois 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.19","name":"1 Rois 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et lorsque le roi mon seigneur sera couch\u00e9 avec ses p\u00e8res, il arrivera que moi et mon fils Salomon nous serons trait\u00e9s comme des coupables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.22","name":"1 Rois 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.20","name":"1 Rois 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Tandis qu\u2019elle parlait encore avec le roi, voici, Nathan le proph\u00e8te arriva.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.23","name":"1 Rois 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.21","name":"1 Rois 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>On l\u2019annon\u00e7a au roi, en disant: Voici Nathan le proph\u00e8te! Il entra en pr\u00e9sence du roi, et se prosterna devant le roi, le visage contre terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.24","name":"1 Rois 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.22","name":"1 Rois 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Et Nathan dit: O roi mon seigneur, c\u2019est donc toi qui as dit: Adonija r\u00e9gnera apr\u00e8s moi, et il s\u2019assi\u00e9ra sur mon tr\u00f4ne!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.25","name":"1 Rois 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.23","name":"1 Rois 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Car il est descendu aujourd\u2019hui, il a tu\u00e9 des b\u0153ufs, des veaux gras et des brebis en quantit\u00e9; et il a invit\u00e9 tous les fils du roi, les chefs de l\u2019arm\u00e9e, et le sacrificateur Abiathar. Et voici, ils mangent et boivent devant lui, et ils disent: Vive le roi Adonija!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.26","name":"1 Rois 1:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.24","name":"1 Rois 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Mais il n\u2019a invit\u00e9 ni moi qui suis ton serviteur, ni le sacrificateur Tsadok, ni Benaja, fils de Jehojada, ni Salomon, ton serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.27","name":"1 Rois 1:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.25","name":"1 Rois 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Est-ce bien par ordre de mon seigneur le roi que cette chose a lieu, et sans que tu aies fait conna\u00eetre \u00e0 ton serviteur qui doit s\u2019asseoir sur le tr\u00f4ne du roi mon seigneur apr\u00e8s lui?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.28","name":"1 Rois 1:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.26","name":"1 Rois 1:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Le roi David r\u00e9pondit: Appelez-moi Bath-Sch\u00e9ba. Elle entra, et se pr\u00e9senta devant le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.29","name":"1 Rois 1:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.27","name":"1 Rois 1:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Et le roi jura, et dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel qui m\u2019a d\u00e9livr\u00e9 de toutes les d\u00e9tresses est vivant!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.30","name":"1 Rois 1:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.28","name":"1 Rois 1:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Ainsi que je te l\u2019ai jur\u00e9 par l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, en disant: Salomon, ton fils, r\u00e9gnera apr\u00e8s moi, et il s\u2019assi\u00e9ra sur mon tr\u00f4ne \u00e0 ma place, ainsi ferai-je aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.31","name":"1 Rois 1:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.29","name":"1 Rois 1:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Bath-Sch\u00e9ba s\u2019inclina le visage contre terre, et se prosterna devant le roi. Et elle dit: Vive \u00e0 jamais mon seigneur le roi David!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.32","name":"1 Rois 1:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.30","name":"1 Rois 1:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.033,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Salomon choisi par David pour lui succ\u00e9der sur le tr\u00f4ne<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 32-40: cf. (1 Ch 23:1; 29:22-25.) 2 Ch 23:9-11. (Pr 20:8. Ec 8:4.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Le roi David dit: Appelez-moi le sacrificateur Tsadok, Nathan le proph\u00e8te, et Benaja, fils de Jehojada. Ils entr\u00e8rent en pr\u00e9sence du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.33","name":"1 Rois 1:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.31","name":"1 Rois 1:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Et le roi leur dit: Prenez avec vous les serviteurs de votre ma\u00eetre, faites monter Salomon, mon fils, sur ma mule, et faites-le descendre \u00e0 Guihon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.34","name":"1 Rois 1:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.32","name":"1 Rois 1:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>L\u00e0, le sacrificateur Tsadok et Nathan le proph\u00e8te l\u2019oindront pour roi sur Isra\u00ebl. Vous sonnerez de la trompette, et vous direz: Vive le roi Salomon!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.35","name":"1 Rois 1:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.33","name":"1 Rois 1:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.35","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:35","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Vous monterez apr\u00e8s lui; il viendra s\u2019asseoir sur mon tr\u00f4ne, et il r\u00e9gnera \u00e0 ma place. C\u2019est lui qui, par mon ordre, sera chef d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.36","name":"1 Rois 1:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.34","name":"1 Rois 1:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.36","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:36","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Benaja, fils de Jehojada, r\u00e9pondit au roi: Amen! Ainsi dise l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de mon seigneur le roi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.37","name":"1 Rois 1:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.35","name":"1 Rois 1:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.37","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:37","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel soit avec Salomon comme il a \u00e9t\u00e9 avec mon seigneur le roi, et qu\u2019il \u00e9l\u00e8ve son tr\u00f4ne au-dessus du tr\u00f4ne de mon seigneur le roi David!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.38","name":"1 Rois 1:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.36","name":"1 Rois 1:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.38","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:38","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Alors le sacrificateur Tsadok descendit avec Nathan le proph\u00e8te, Benaja, fils de Jehojada, les K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens et les P\u00e9l\u00e9thiens; ils firent monter Salomon sur la mule du roi David, et ils le men\u00e8rent \u00e0 Guihon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.39","name":"1 Rois 1:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.37","name":"1 Rois 1:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.39","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:39","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Le sacrificateur Tsadok prit la corne d\u2019huile dans la tente, et il oignit Salomon. On sonna de la trompette, et tout le peuple dit: Vive le roi Salomon!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.40","name":"1 Rois 1:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.38","name":"1 Rois 1:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.40","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:40","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Tout le peuple monta apr\u00e8s lui, et le peuple jouait de la fl\u00fbte et se livrait \u00e0 une grande joie; la terre s\u2019\u00e9branlait par leurs cris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.41","name":"1 Rois 1:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.39","name":"1 Rois 1:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.41","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:41","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.042,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 41-53: cf. 1 R 2:13, etc. (Pr 21:6. J\u00e9 17:11.) Job 5:12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Ce bruit fut entendu d\u2019Adonija et de tous les convi\u00e9s qui \u00e9taient avec lui, au moment o\u00f9 ils finissaient de manger. Joab, entendant le son de la trompette, dit: Pourquoi ce bruit de la ville en tumulte?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.42","name":"1 Rois 1:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.40","name":"1 Rois 1:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.42","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:42","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Il parlait encore lorsque Jonathan, fils du sacrificateur Abiathar, arriva. Et Adonija dit: Approche, car tu es un vaillant homme, et tu apportes de bonnes nouvelles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.43","name":"1 Rois 1:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.41","name":"1 Rois 1:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.43","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:43","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>Oui! R\u00e9pondit Jonathan \u00e0 Adonija, notre seigneur le roi David a fait Salomon roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.44","name":"1 Rois 1:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.42","name":"1 Rois 1:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.44","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:44","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>Il a envoy\u00e9 avec lui le sacrificateur Tsadok, Nathan le proph\u00e8te, Benaja, fils de Jehojada, les K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens et les P\u00e9l\u00e9thiens, et ils l\u2019ont fait monter sur la mule du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.45","name":"1 Rois 1:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.43","name":"1 Rois 1:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.45","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:45","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>Le sacrificateur Tsadok et Nathan le proph\u00e8te l\u2019ont oint pour roi \u00e0 Guihon. De l\u00e0 ils sont remont\u00e9s en se livrant \u00e0 la joie, et la ville a \u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e9mue: c\u2019est l\u00e0 le bruit que vous avez entendu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.46","name":"1 Rois 1:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.44","name":"1 Rois 1:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.46","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:46","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Salomon s\u2019est m\u00eame assis sur le tr\u00f4ne royal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.47","name":"1 Rois 1:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.45","name":"1 Rois 1:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.47","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:47","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Et les serviteurs du roi sont venus pour b\u00e9nir notre seigneur le roi David, en disant: Que ton Dieu rende le nom de Salomon plus c\u00e9l\u00e8bre que ton nom, et qu\u2019il \u00e9l\u00e8ve son tr\u00f4ne au-dessus de ton tr\u00f4ne! Et le roi s\u2019est prostern\u00e9 sur son lit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.48","name":"1 Rois 1:48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.46","name":"1 Rois 1:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.48","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:48","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Voici encore ce qu\u2019a dit le roi: B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui m\u2019a donn\u00e9 aujourd\u2019hui un successeur sur mon tr\u00f4ne, et qui m\u2019a permis de le voir!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.49","name":"1 Rois 1:49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.47","name":"1 Rois 1:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.49","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:49","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>Tous les convi\u00e9s d\u2019Adonija furent saisis d\u2019\u00e9pouvante; ils se lev\u00e8rent et s\u2019en all\u00e8rent chacun de son c\u00f4t\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.50","name":"1 Rois 1:50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.48","name":"1 Rois 1:48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.50","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:50","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>Adonija eut peur de Salomon; il se leva aussi, s\u2019en alla, et saisit les cornes de l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.51","name":"1 Rois 1:51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.49","name":"1 Rois 1:49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.51","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:51","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>On vint dire \u00e0 Salomon: Voici, Adonija a peur du roi Salomon, et il a saisi les cornes de l\u2019autel, en disant: Que le roi Salomon me jure aujourd\u2019hui qu\u2019il ne fera point mourir son serviteur par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.52","name":"1 Rois 1:52","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.50","name":"1 Rois 1:50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.52","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:52","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.053,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup>Salomon dit: S\u2019il se montre un honn\u00eate homme, il ne tombera pas \u00e0 terre un de ses cheveux; mais s\u2019il se trouve en lui de la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9, il mourra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.53","name":"1 Rois 1:53","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.51","name":"1 Rois 1:51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.53","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 1:53","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.1.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup>Et le roi Salomon envoya des gens, qui le firent descendre de l\u2019autel. Il vint se prosterner devant le roi Salomon, et Salomon lui dit: Va dans ta maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1","name":"1 Rois 1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.2.1","name":"1 Rois 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.52","name":"1 Rois 1:52","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb987d3f7.64339385');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb987d3f7.64339385\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb987d3f7.64339385","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb987d3f7.64339385'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb987d3f7.64339385\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}